**RULES:**
- Always set `overflow-wrap: anywhere` and `white-space: pre-wrap` on bubble — handles URLs, code, and user line breaks.
- Always cap `.msg-stack { max-width: min(72%, 480px); }` — prevents single-line bubbles from spanning the full width on desktop.
- Always use `textContent` (not `innerHTML`) when inserting user text — prevents XSS.
- The autoresize handler must call `el.style.height = 'auto'` BEFORE measuring `scrollHeight`, otherwise the height only grows, never shrinks.
- Enter sends, Shift+Enter newline — that's the universal expectation; do not invert.
- Avatars belong on the receive side only by convention (your own messages don't need a self-avatar).
- Timestamps as `<time>` element with locale formatting; do NOT hard-code 'PM' suffix (i18n).
- Read receipts: ✓ = sent, ✓✓ = delivered, ✓✓ in accent color = read. Optional but standard.
